        full, hackathon details are sent to the team host</h5>
      <br />
      <a href="/api/project"><button
          class="homeSignUpBtn text-center"
          style="width: 15rem"
        >View Projects</button></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  
  <br> 
